text: Clypeosectus is a genus of sea snails, marine gastropod mollusks in the family Lepetodrilidae. ==Species== Species within the genus Clypeosectus include: * Clypeosectus curvus McLean, 1989 * Clypeosectus delectus McLean, 1989 ==References== ==External links== * Category:Lepetodrilidae
title: Clypeosectus
